text: Dhaghano Bozdar is a town and Union Council of Tando Allahyar District in the Sindh Province of Pakistan. The Union Council has 56,892 people. It is part of Tando Allahyar Taluka. It is in the west of the district. ==References== Category:Union councils of Tando Allahyar District
title: Dhaghano Bozdar
